Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath

Interface Materializable<T extends Type>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanLiteralPath, BooleanPath, CodingLiteralPath, CodingPath, DateLiteralPath, DatePath, DateTimeLiteralPath, DateTimePath, DecimalLiteralPath, DecimalPath, IntegerLiteralPath, IntegerPath, StringLiteralPath, StringPath, TimeLiteralPath, TimePath
    public interface Materializable<T extends Type>
    Designates an expression that is capable of being extracted from a Spark dataset and materialized back into a value featured within a result, e.g. for use in a grouping label or as part of an extract.
    Author:
    John Grimes
